NAME
    Template::Plugin::JA::Fold - Template plugin that interface to
    Lingua::JA::Fold

SYNOPSIS
      [% USE JA::Fold %]
      [% foo | fold(10,'full-width') | html | html_line_break %]

DESCRIPTION
    Template::Plugin::JA::Fold is plugin that interface to Lingua::JA::Fold
    for Template-Toolkit

AUTHOR
    Hideaki Ohno <hide.o.j55 {at} gmail.com>

SEE ALSO
    Template Template::Plugin Lingua::JA::Fold

